2.1.2 Installing the CLI
------------------------

The ‘eve’ CLI ships as a Python package inside this repository.  On a
fresh clone it bootstraps itself automatically via ‘scripts/run-cli.sh’
using the pre-built wheel in ‘cli/dist/’ — no ‘uv’ or Python package
manager required at runtime.

   To install ‘eve’ globally so ‘M-x eve-transcribe’ can find it:

     pip install cli/dist/eve_cli-*.whl
     # or with uv:
     uv pip install cli/dist/eve_cli-*.whl

   Verify it works:

     eve doctor --json


