14.4 Dependencies
=================

Hard requirements:

   • Emacs 29.1+
   • mpv (playback)
   • ‘eve’ CLI (transcription and rendering)

   Optional:

   • ‘hydra’ — enables the ‘?’ graphical cheatsheet popup


