Appendix A Appendix A: TJM v1.1 Specification
*********************************************

The normative TJM v1.1 specification is maintained in ‘docs/tjm-spec.md’
in the repository.  It defines:

   • The complete JSON schema for ‘.tjm.json’ files.
   • The tick-based timing model and its relationship to real-time
     seconds.
   • The edit overlay structure (‘edit’ field on segments and words).
   • The deterministic render contract that ‘eve text-edit’ implements.
   • Migration paths from earlier TJM versions.

   To read the specification, open ‘docs/tjm-spec.md’ in the repository
or visit the repository at <https://github.com/behaghel/eve.el>.


